<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-38-0184 </DOCNO><TEXT>Some problems of IAEA member states concerning radioactive waste and spentnuclear fuel handling are analyzed. The technique of removal of high-levelradioactive wastes and {alpha}-bearing wastes as well as the problemsconcerning spent nuclear fuel conditioning are considered. The importanceof governmental policy, public opinion and international cooperationfor radioactive waste handling is noted.</TEXT></DOC>